data.description: HORSE FARM! Come see this 6.68 ac working horse farm today. This farm has been used for boarding, teaching riding lessons, etc. Or, let it be your private equestrian oasis in the pines! This property boasts a 2 BR/2 BA home attached to a 3-stall barn with concrete aisleway. There is a full hayloft with the potential of being converted into a 3rd bedroom. There are three fenced paddocks with lots of room for you to bring your horses. (Please note, sellers are in process of repairing fencing). This property is beautifully secluded yet conveniently located, less than 1/2 mile from Union Pines High School! This property really has all the potential in the world! Come see it today!
